b'Emergency Whistle'
b'Get attention fast! Designed by Search & Rescue professionals, the UIC Ready\xc2\xa0Emergency Whistle\xc2\xa0utilizes a 3-chamber design to produce multiple frequency blasts up to 120 decibels, giving you the best chance of being HEARD and RESCUED in an emergency. Emergency whistles are great in survival situations, natural disaster situations, crime prevention, scaring animals and/or any other potential threats. A loud blast from our whistle is an excellent signal for help, easily heard by UIC Police, local law enforcement, campus security and others nearby. Gear up, Get UIC Ready! Stop by the\xc2\xa0Office of Preparedness and Response\xc2\xa0today to pick up your whistle!'
b'\xc2\xa0'
b''
b'Active Threat Scroll Pen\n'
b'In high-demand! The active threat scroll pen is always on-hand to share how best to prepare for, respond to, and recover from this event. At your fingertips, you\xe2\x80\x99ll know who to contact if you witness suspicious behavior, how to build a room barricade, and how to assist your peers during any emergency situation.\xc2\xa0'
b'\xc2\xa0'
b''
b'Backpack tags\n'
b'You\xe2\x80\x99ve seen them and we\xe2\x80\x99ve got them. Backpack tags go with you everywhere and clip easily on and off student backpacks. These tags have a little of everything that\xe2\x80\x99s important when you need it. Color-coded, they instruct where to access emergency updates, inform who to call in a crisis, share medical and emergency contact information, and more!\xc2\xa0'
b''
b'Active Threat Wallet Cards\n'
b'Do you know what to do? Active Threat Wallet Cards show your options and what to do. Get one for your wallet to protect yourself and those around you.\xc2\xa0'
b'Products can be picked up at the Paulina St. Building - 1140 S. Paulina St., Suite 109. For more information please contact us at ready@uic.edu.\xc2\xa0'
